<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-06-0768 </DOCNO><TEXT>In this article the author provides perspective for the specific problemsthat are discussed in other works by reviewing the wide sweep of changesthat have affected the Petroleum industry over the past 20 years. Thesechanges include environmental policies and their influence on Americanpolitics, the adjustment to the free market following decades of pricecontrols, cost efficiency, progress in technology and economics.</TEXT></DOC>